# 🧠 Scrabble AI using Reinforcement Learning and Pattern Recognition

A complete Scrabble Artificial Intelligence project developed in Python.

This project demonstrates how Reinforcement Learning (Q-Learning), Pattern Recognition, heuristic search, and traditional game algorithms can be combined to build an intelligent Scrabble player capable of learning better moves over time.

---

# Project Overview

The goal of this project is to create an AI agent that can:

- Play Scrabble against a human
- Generate legal words
- Evaluate board positions
- Learn from previous games
- Improve its strategy using Reinforcement Learning

Unlike a traditional Scrabble program that follows fixed rules, this AI stores knowledge inside a Q-table and gradually improves after playing many games.

