# Q-Learning Formula

The project implements

```
Q(s,a) ← Q(s,a)
       + α [ reward
       + γ max(Q(s',a'))
       − Q(s,a)]
```

Where

- α = Learning Rate
- γ = Discount Factor
- reward = Immediate reward

